 Crazy XP (4 Enchanters, 1 Cleric) Group in PoI</span><hr size=1> Had a really crazy XP group on the Planes of Innovation over the weekend: 4 Enchanters, 1 Cleric.<br>
<br>
All Enchanters had charmed pets up (and not those wimpy Dire Charm pets).  Having 4 pets that dish out damage like those broken-down trash heaps was AMAZING.  Enchanters had berserker shields up to soften the blows when charm inevitably broke, but all the enchanters would chain stun until the pet was back under control.  Cleric was there for lil heals now and then.<br>
<br>
It's the second time I've been in a group with multiple enchanters charming pets, but this one topped the cake but not having any other class save the cleric.  Very weird, very bizarre, but it landed me a level and a ding, so I mark it as a great success! <p><BR><I><font face="John Handy LET" color="#FFFF00" size="3"><B>Shantar</B></FONT></I><BR>
<font color="#FFEE00" size="2">Keeper of the Faith</FONT><BR>
<font color="#FFEE00" size="2">Lord Magistrate & Guild Leader</FONT><BR>
<font color="#FFEE00" size="2">Avengers in Faith</FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=deraedreamer>Derae Dreamer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(1/28/03 11:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm57.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crazy XP (4 Enchanters, 1 Cleric) Group in PoI</span><hr size=1> Try working a druid in there if u can at times, they help sooooo much with charming because their snare lasts longer than our charm so a quick run off to the side a recast an no one gets hurt except the mobs <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  its lovely.<br>
<br>
Druid enchanter is one of the nicest duo's in game if u struggling for a group just find yourself a friendly druid, (rangers work too if u stuck)<br>
<br>
Did you speed your pets? <br>
<br>
Der<br>
